OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780924280
OL,3,CPlymouth tenants without hot water and
OL,4,Cheating for weeks in 'unstable' flats
OL,6,FSam Blackledge reports
OL,8,FResidents who were forced to leave a
OL,9,Fblock of 'unstable' flats in Plymouth
OL,10,Ffor more than two months say they have
OL,11,Fno heating or hot water since
OL,12,Freturning home last week.
OL,14,FEvolution Cove was evacuated in March
OL,15,Fafter it was deemed at risk of
OL,16,Fcollapse.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780924280
OL,3,CPlymouth tenants without hot water and
OL,4,Cheating for weeks in 'unstable' flats
OL,6,FFinally back home, those living there
OL,7,Fare now being directed to a nearby
OL,8,Fleisure centre to have showers, and it
OL,9,Fcould be up to eight weeks until
OL,10,Feveryone's gas supplies are restored.
OL,12,FThe building's owners have apologised
OL,13,Fand say they are working on a solution.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780924280
OL,3,CPlymouth tenants without hot water and
OL,4,Cheating for weeks in 'unstable' flats
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV West Country on his
OL,7,Ffirst day back in his apartment since
OL,8,FMarch, tenant Jon Dingle said: "I
OL,9,Fcurrently have no electricity, no gas,
OL,10,Fand they can't say when we're going to
OL,11,Fhave the gas turned back on. So I am
OL,12,Fcurrently without hot water or a
OL,13,Fshower."
OL,15,FThe building's management company,
OL,16,FCentrick, has apologised to residents
OL,17,Fand told them they can visit a nearby
OL,18,Fcommunity centre - a 15 minute walk
OL,19,Faway - to use the showers.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780924280
OL,3,CPlymouth tenants without hot water and
OL,4,Cheating for weeks in 'unstable' flats
OL,6,FJon said: "I don't think it's going to
OL,7,Fbe manageable really, it's not a
OL,8,Fviable solution.
OL,10,F"My son who lives with me, who is
OL,11,Fautistic, still doesn't want to return
OL,12,Fhome, that's going to be too much for
OL,13,Fhim to deal with."
OL,15,FBack on March 20th, residents of
OL,16,FEvolution Cove were told to leave as
OL,17,Fthe building was unsafe.
OL,19,FOn April 17th, nearby homes were also
OL,20,Fevacuated and an exclusion zone was
OL,21,Fput in place.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780924280
OL,3,CPlymouth tenants without hot water and
OL,4,Cheating for weeks in 'unstable' flats
OL,6,FLater, an engineer's report revealed
OL,7,F'widespread cracking' to the
OL,8,Fbuilding's foundations. A temporary
OL,9,Fsolution was found, and people began
OL,10,Fto return home at the end of May.
OL,12,FThe building's owners, Grey GR, and
OL,13,Fthe management company, Centrick, have
OL,14,Fapologised. But Jon and other tenants
OL,15,Fsay they are not impressed and believe
OL,16,Fresidents should receive compensation.
OL,18,F"I don't think it's been handled well
OL,19,Fat all," Jon said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780924280
OL,3,CPlymouth tenants without hot water and
OL,4,Cheating for weeks in 'unstable' flats
OL,6,F"Right from the get-go, I didn't
OL,7,Frealise it would be this long before
OL,8,Fwe could return.
OL,10,F"Whenever I've tried to communicate
OL,11,Fwith Centrick, I've just had nothing
OL,12,Fback.
OL,14,F"We've been put into this situation in
OL,15,Fthe first place, which is no fault of
OL,16,Four own.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780924280
OL,3,CPlymouth tenants without hot water and
OL,4,Cheating for weeks in 'unstable' flats
OL,6,F"I've been paying my rent, I've been
OL,7,Fpaying my bills, I've been doing
OL,8,Feverything that's expected of me as a
OL,9,Fgood tenant, yet we've been thrown
OL,10,Finto this situation for a period of
OL,11,Falmost two months and it's not been
OL,12,Fany of our doing."
OL,14,FCentrick has written to residents
OL,15,Fsaying the work to restore gas
OL,16,Fsupplies could take anywhere between
OL,17,Ftwo and eight weeks to complete.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
