OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780924280
OL,3,CPlymouth tenants without hot water and
OL,4,Cheating for weeks in 'unstable' flats
OL,6,FThey say temporary accommodation can
OL,7,Fbe extended further if needed, and
OL,8,Fthey have apologised for the
OL,9,Fdisruption.
OL,11,FA spokesman for Grey GR, the
OL,12,Fbuilding's owner, said: "The temporary
OL,13,Fpropping works at Evolution Cove were
OL,14,Fcompleted to schedule.
OL,16,F"However, there have been some
OL,17,Funexpected challenges with restoring
OL,18,Fgas supply to individual apartments.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780924280
OL,3,CPlymouth tenants without hot water and
OL,4,Cheating for weeks in 'unstable' flats
OL,6,F"Central gas to the building has been
OL,7,Frestored, however, inspectors
OL,8,Fidentified unforeseen concerns within
OL,9,Findividual apartments ` in respect of
OL,10,Fpipework, appliances, and maintenance.
OL,12,F"We understand this is frustrating for
OL,13,Fresidents and have arranged access to
OL,14,Fshowering and welfare facilities at a
OL,15,Flocal leisure facility for all
OL,16,Fresidents."
OL,26,@xD@KO]
